ctrl+c.....This is the shortcut to copy anything that you highlighted


ctrl+v.....This is the shortcut to paste the subgect you highlighted



ctrl+x.....This is the shortcut to cut the subjet you highlighted



alt+tab.....This helps to Switch between programs



Ctrl + Shift + Esc.....This opens the task manager



Windows Key + Break....This opens system properties



Windows Key + F....opens search for files and folders



ctrl+t.....This helps open a new tab



ctrl+shift+t....This helps to reopen a new tab



alt+tab....This helps to switch programs



ctrl+d.....This helps to bookmark a website